OL,3,CDog named in memory of care home
OL,4,Cresident who was defrauded by manager
OL,6,FA rescue dog has been named in memory
OL,7,Fof a victim who lost thousands of
OL,8,Fpounds when he was defrauded by a care
OL,9,Fhome worker in Bristol.
OL,11,FThe 83-year-old animal lover, who died
OL,12,Fbefore the case came to court, wanted
OL,13,Fhis savings to be left to two animal
OL,14,Fcharities. That's now been possible
OL,15,Fwith the recovery of the defrauded
OL,16,Fmoney.
OL,18,FBristol Animal Rescue Centre (BARC)
OL,19,Fand the RSPCA will receive more than
OL,20,F#46,000 in honour of Mr Chandler's
OL,21,Fmemory.
