OL,6,FIn recognition of Mr Chandler's
OL,7,Fposthumous donation, BARC honoured his
OL,8,Fmemory and love of animals by naming
OL,9,Fone of their newest resident dogs, an
OL,10,Fadorable Yorkshire terrier, after him.
OL,11,FIt will be known as Mr Chandler.
OL,13,FA spokesman from Bristol ARC charity
OL,14,Fsaid: "We are so grateful to those
OL,15,Flike Mr Chandler for their generosity,
OL,16,Fas well as the Financial Investigation
OL,17,FUnit for ensuring his wishes were
OL,18,Ffulfilled.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
