OL,6,F"To honour him, we have named one of
OL,7,Four newest residents after him a sweet
OL,8,FYorkshire terrier - bound to be a
OL,9,Fpopular boy!
OL,11,F"Mr. Chandler's legacy donation will
OL,12,Fbe a lasting support for thousands of
OL,13,Fanimals that come into our care, and
OL,14,Fwe hope it inspires others to consider
OL,15,Fleaving a gift in their will to
OL,16,Fsupport animals in need."
