OL,3,CDog named in memory of care home
OL,4,Cresident who was defrauded by manager
OL,6,FCare home manager Nikola Penevski was
OL,7,Fcharged in March last year with fraud
OL,8,Fby abuse of position and was sentenced
OL,9,Fto two years and three months in
OL,10,Fprison after he pleaded guilty to
OL,11,Ftaking more than #46,000. He had taken
OL,12,Fmoney from the victim's bank account.
OL,14,FSadly, Mr Chandler died in 2023,
OL,15,Fbefore the case went to court, with no
OL,16,Fliving family.
OL,18,FThe missing money was recovered
OL,19,Fthrough the work of the Financial
OL,20,FInvestigation Unit.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
