OL,6,FJohanna Buck, from the FIU, said: "Our
OL,7,Frole is to confiscate money and
OL,8,Fbelongings earned by individuals to
OL,9,Fprevent them from benefiting from
OL,10,Ftheir crimes.
OL,12,F"In this case, while it is a great
OL,13,Fsadness that Mr Chandler died before
OL,14,Fhe could get his stolen money back, we
OL,15,Fare glad that we could honour the
OL,16,Fwishes laid out in his will and donate
OL,17,Fthe seized money to his chosen
OL,18,Fcharities.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
