OL,4,Cresident who was defrauded by manager
OL,6,F"I would like to recognise the
OL,7,FFinancial Investigator for this case,
OL,8,FNikki Matthews, who worked tirelessly
OL,9,Fto ensure the confiscation order went
OL,10,Fthrough and to arrange the donations.
OL,12,F"Her work, and the work of the unit as
OL,13,Fa whole, strives to ensure that
OL,14,Fcriminals do not prosper from their
OL,15,Foffences and return the funds to their
OL,16,Frightful owners where possible."
