OL,6,FAfter the sentencing of Penevski, it
OL,7,Fbecame apparent he'd used his position
OL,8,Fas a manager to receive additional
OL,9,Ffunds from staff and other residents
OL,10,Fand their families at the care home.
OL,12,FIn July this year, the confiscation
OL,13,Forder was made at Bristol Crown Court
OL,14,Fwhich stated Penevski made almost
OL,15,F#58,000 from his crimes,. He was
OL,16,Fordered to pay more than #46,000 to
OL,17,Fthe victims.
